Title: Non-commutative geometry and covariance

quantum tensorsAuthors: J.A. de Azcarraga, P.P. Kulish, F. Rodenas

Comments: Lecture delivered (by J.A.) at the 3rd Colloquium `Quantum groups and

Physics', Prague, June 1994. To appear in the proceedings (Czechoslovak J.Phys.)Journal-ref: Czech. J. Phys. 44 (1994) 981

Reflection and braid equations for rank two $q$-tensors are derived from thecovariance properties of quantum vectors by using the $R$-matrix formalism.